<div class="py-16 bg-charcoal border-t border-b border-gold border-opacity-10">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-5vw">
    <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-12 lg:gap-20">
      
      {# Halal Seal #}
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center">
        <div class="w-36 h-36 rounded-full border-4 border-gold flex flex-col items-center justify-center relative flex-shrink-0">
          <div class="absolute inset-1.5 border border-gold border-opacity-30 rounded-full"></div>
          <span class="font-display text-4xl font-bold text-gold text-center leading-tight">حلال</span>
          <span class="text-xs text-smoke uppercase tracking-widest mt-2">CERTIFIED HALAL</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      {# Content #}
      <div class="flex-1 text-right lg:text-right">
        <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-cream mb-4 font-display">
          الذبح على السنّة والشريعة
        </h3>
        
        <p class="text-smoke leading-relaxed mb-6 text-base">
          جميع منتجاتنا مذبوحة وفق الضوابط الشرعية الإسلامية، معتمدة من جهات رقابية دولية معترف بها، 
          مع توثيق كامل لكل دفعة من المصدر إلى التسليم.
        </p>

        {# Certifications #}
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 justify-end">
          <span class="border border-gold border-opacity-25 text-gold text-xs px-3 py-1.5 font-latin uppercase tracking-widest">SASO Certified</span>
          <span class="border border-gold border-opacity-25 text-gold text-xs px-3 py-1.5 font-latin uppercase tracking-widest">SFDA Approved</span>
          <span class="border border-gold border-opacity-25 text-gold text-xs px-3 py-1.5 font-latin uppercase tracking-widest">International Halal</span>
          <span class="border border-gold border-opacity-25 text-gold text-xs px-3 py-1.5 font-latin uppercase tracking-widest">ISO 22000</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
